<div class='whiteout'>
	<div id='empty'></div>
	<header class='home'>
		<div class='container'>
			<div class='row'>
				<div class='span12'>
					<h1>How it works</h1>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class='row steps'>
				<div class='span4'>
					<h2>
						1
						<small>Publish your project</small>
					</h2>
					<p>Good news! You've already done this bit (or you're about to). Now let's make your data easier for people to find, use and share.</p>

				</div>

				<div class='span4'>
					<h2>
						<small>Create new user certificate</small>
					</h2>
					<p>Fill up a simple form and get your new user certificate</p>
				</div>

				<div class='span4 last'>
					<h2>
						3
						<small>Share it with a certificate</small>
					</h2>
					<p>Add the certificate to your app's website and share it with the world.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</header>

	<div class='container' id='main'>
		<div class='home-header-buttons'>
			<div class='row'>

				<div class='span4'>
					<p class='logo'>ODI</p>
				</div>
				<div class='span4'>
					<%= link_to 'Create new user certificate', new_project_path, class: "btn btn-large btn-primary" %> 
					<!--<a href="/projects#new"  data-toggle="modal" role="button">Create a user certificate</a>-->
				</div>
				<div class='span4'>
					<a href="/projects" class="btn btn-large btn-primary">Browse certificates</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class='main'>
			<div class='row'>
				<div class='span6'>
					<div class='video-container'>
						<iframe allowfullscreen='allowfullscreen' frameborder='0' height='315' src='https://www.youtube.com/embed/_k5pQxeQq9w' width='560'></iframe>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class='span6 homepage-about-content'>
					<h2 class='about-certificate'>
						<a href="/about/index">What does a certificate look like?</a>
					</h2>
					<p class='about-certificate'>It's a badge that links to a description of your open data. The description explores things like how often it's updated, what format it's in, who and where it came from.</p>
					<a href="/about/index" class="about-certificate">Find out more</a>

					<h2 class='about-odi'>
						<a href="/contact">Who are the ODI?</a>
					</h2>
					<p class='about-odi'>We're the <a href="http://theodi.org">Open Data Institute</a>. We help people unlock supply and demand for open data and share this value with everyone.</p>
					<a href="/contact" class="about-odi">Get in touch</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>